{"id": "ChIJvUEvXFvDwoARl9BcjiTGrQs", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 222, "displayName": {"text": "The Gourmet Cobbler Factory", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Unfussy, longstanding family-owned bakery featuring Southern-style cobblers & pies.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJvUEvXFvDwoARl9BcjiTGrQs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WaGVscG9aVTFxV2tGTVJuTTBWRTFmZEhkV09XYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "This little hole in the wall does cobbler right. I got the ribs meal and a peach cobbler. I got mac and cheese and beans with the ribs, unfortunately the mac and cheese was the best part of the dinner. But the cobbler was sweet, and very sizable so it can easily feed two people as a dessert", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This little hole in the wall does cobbler right. I got the ribs meal and a peach cobbler. I got mac and cheese and beans with the ribs, unfortunately the mac and cheese was the best part of the dinner. But the cobbler was sweet, and very sizable so it can easily feed two people as a dessert", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alex DeMartino", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107620400605221358125/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZL9hCL4qQaKAp6KEz1ZOnbsMUy4q-S2_JDOauWzLnCkW-ySA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-27T23:41:12.351866068Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WaGVscG9aVTFxV2tGTVJuTTBWRTFmZEhkV09XYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WaGVscG9aVTFxV2tGTVJuTTBWRTFmZEhkV09XYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c35b5c2f41bd:0xbadc6248e5cd097"}, {"name": "places/ChIJvUEvXFvDwoARl9BcjiTGrQs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ob1YydFZhalJRTjJOUE9VTlBPRzlvY1ZWWFYzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Very small place that's been there for decades. They make the best cobbler that you can buy. They also make barbecue ribs that are so tender and delicious. Their barbecue sauce is some of the best I've ever tasted.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Very small place that's been there for decades. They make the best cobbler that you can buy. They also make barbecue ribs that are so tender and delicious. Their barbecue sauce is some of the best I've ever tasted.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "David Alegria", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100988311508019270910/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLIN-KPVzH4PMGV5EY3SLnof_c5XbX83aiNmjJO7dtOsrGg4g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-26T04:54:18.518776534Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ob1YydFZhalJRTjJOUE9VTlBPRzlvY1ZWWFYzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ob1YydFZhalJRTjJOUE9VTlBPRzlvY1ZWWFYzYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c35b5c2f41bd:0xbadc6248e5cd097"}, {"name": "places/ChIJvUEvXFvDwoARl9BcjiTGrQs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsalVsRmtObEZPVUZaM1ltOVFZMWh4VldOM2MxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "A unassuming little shop tucked around the corner. You’d miss it if you weren’t looking. I love the smaller portions of cobbler so you can enjoy it for a date night while it’s nice and fresh! It’s definitely a grab and go place. I’ve heard great things about the gumbo. Can’t wait to try that next! Peach cobbler and berry cobbler were both delicious!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "A unassuming little shop tucked around the corner. You’d miss it if you weren’t looking. I love the smaller portions of cobbler so you can enjoy it for a date night while it’s nice and fresh! It’s definitely a grab and go place. I’ve heard great things about the gumbo. Can’t wait to try that next! Peach cobbler and berry cobbler were both delicious!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Leondra Graves", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114159060133125632044/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiJhBlZvtsnRVWPTULdIWo56X-K4kp0ml3kTHo8ocGwtKTeh9A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-20T05:37:54.620440678Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsalVsRmtObEZPVUZaM1ltOVFZMWh4VldOM2MxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsalVsRmtObEZPVUZaM1ltOVFZMWh4VldOM2MxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c35b5c2f41bd:0xbadc6248e5cd097"}, {"name": "places/ChIJvUEvXFvDwoARl9BcjiTGrQs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25BNVIzUlVPRmx6YkhGeVNFczFaa05vZFd0aGVXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Cobbler is great. Very limited seating outside, so it really is a take out place. They also have bbq, but I haven't tried it yet.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Cobbler is great. Very limited seating outside, so it really is a take out place. They also have bbq, but I haven't tried it yet.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sherman Tieng", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101160382451905160916/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8ykjrITCOfydd3vcyAOTkzmpNrup8-8oRlWJyToRPg6l57w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-10T22:54:29.893694630Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25BNVIzUlVPRmx6YkhGeVNFczFaa05vZFd0aGVXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25BNVIzUlVPRmx6YkhGeVNFczFaa05vZFd0aGVXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c35b5c2f41bd:0xbadc6248e5cd097"}, {"name": "places/ChIJvUEvXFvDwoARl9BcjiTGrQs/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURKMmVlMkFREAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 years ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Located on a sleepier and quieter side of Pasadena, The Gourmet Cobbler Factory is run by a nice old Black couple. Their other business is Clifton's BBQ which is two store fronts merged together. It is tucked away on the side of a building and initially is hard to find but there is tons of street parking. My mom and I saw a Huell Howser special on them a while back and for sure this couple has been baking cobblers and bbq for over thirty years now at least.\n\nI like getting their cobblers and taking it home to eat with some ice cream. Just two scoops over the 4x6 pies is enough as a good dessert. The bbq is good too and arguably better than Gus' and Lucille's. Would the pies be more if you got it from Marie Callender's? Of course it would just like any other major restaurant but the charm of the Gourmet Cobble Factory is not just the cobblers and bbq but getting to support local businesses -- our mom and pop businesses especially black owned. If you're in the area, stop by the Gourmet Cobbler Factory and pick up some cobblers and bbq.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Located on a sleepier and quieter side of Pasadena, The Gourmet Cobbler Factory is run by a nice old Black couple. Their other business is Clifton's BBQ which is two store fronts merged together. It is tucked away on the side of a building and initially is hard to find but there is tons of street parking. My mom and I saw a Huell Howser special on them a while back and for sure this couple has been baking cobblers and bbq for over thirty years now at least.\n\nI like getting their cobblers and taking it home to eat with some ice cream. Just two scoops over the 4x6 pies is enough as a good dessert. The bbq is good too and arguably better than Gus' and Lucille's. Would the pies be more if you got it from Marie Callender's? Of course it would just like any other major restaurant but the charm of the Gourmet Cobble Factory is not just the cobblers and bbq but getting to support local businesses -- our mom and pop businesses especially black owned. If you're in the area, stop by the Gourmet Cobbler Factory and pick up some cobblers and bbq.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jacqueline Lee", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101284053694342262615/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVj2bbkMkCQJGAaHRjb8isb0K1IQjDKA-6m9H9HWh4mVsO0fP1I=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2023-07-20T05:50:11.896709Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURKMmVlMkFREAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURKMmVlMkFREAE!2m1!1s0x80c2c35b5c2f41bd:0xbadc6248e5cd097"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJvUEvXFvDwoARl9BcjiTGrQs/photos/AWCwyditjmOPtpUZPaSZ6rahfGMLnOWyY-pEr17Yt2aGFpwDnKLuTmANHMG9ZJ0DU15thgfe4SS43ORk1GUrZS5VMbazf6rt71beUCwis72ZDaD6DC41dMmQeppuwBIoeoLdF5_vpCdXgMDMwDnQZzatEYurU5tsaMyqmovqq7tfxuI6zru621Kr9Twy6hRvnIA7HPYMrWaTvt_lWjiXRmZyutP4nD8OBF9Wjh55F2Tpre6VXnwOfFF9uYdwwtdK8KpGxoLSbkDMD_2hPHZU_ZPiaLma8JapLx-O03wj5iMFdC6dviiB77oKIGXc8Oy8LzKsCph1VUa51GpeZS-WrRMmrkjUN7uFRjef-w03U8qxrf7xwgxB7gsjF7MPWNveiudRaHxBNL0vYiIkYTmqnZuQfgathy8qnuP_nQEG1Jg4Nu1TjiO3", "widthPx": 3898, "heightPx": 2134, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Luis Peña", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/113016019479202310952", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLjfWLyYM5opSAQZkrmwuTv0WFxjTfYu_T1mX9Zlvxw16ygcQ=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgICEtuzoggE&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_